{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"body":"Implemented in commit 74dd64bdb (Change-Id I0e8af6ed). Pure-intercept CLI rebar verify-commit-ticket (verify_commit.py) with EXPECTED_FORMAT single-source constant (CLI error + --help + docs, pinned by a doc-drift test); path-safe extraction (traversal guard); resolution via resolve_ticket_id (alias/full/short/Jira). Config verify.require_ticket_for_commit (env override) enabled in rebar.toml. CI require-ticket job in gerrit-verify.yaml (idempotent mount + retry + distinguishable infra error + REBAR_TRACKER_DIR) wired into needs -> Verified-1 on failure. Docs: commit-ticket-trailer.md + CONTRIBUTING + CLAUDE + config.md. Tests: 23 pass (test_verify_commit_ticket.py) + help-overview parity contract intact. Gates: ruff+format+mypy clean; full suite 3882 passed (sole failure is the deselected integration/live-jira test -> bug fb50-f26a-d6fc-44c7). Dogfood: HEAD passes its own gate (crusty-dryad-spray -> 263d). Decision: no first-element-only rule (documented)."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1783050582915053001,"uuid":"d5250f12-f512-4470-b9b3-1a872d7963e2"}